    <h3 align=center id=qname>Tunare Initiate</h3><hr size=1>
	 <table width=100% cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 border=0>
	 <tr><td valign=top>
	 <table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 border=0 align=left>
	 <tr><td><b>Starts in:</b></td><td><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Faydwer/Felwithe.htm'>Felwithe</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Who:</b></td><td><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=829>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Rating:</b></td><td>Not so Good (2.78)</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Estimated Time:</b></td><td></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Minimum Level:</b></td><td>8</td></tr><tr><td><b>Best Class:</b></td><td>Cler Drui</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Quest Items:</b></span><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2754">Bone Chips</a></li><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=5653">Ghast Heart</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Related Creatures:</b></span><li>Ghast</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><span id=rt><b>Related Quests:</b></span><li><a href=quest.html?quest=1253>Tunare Disciple</a></li></ul></td></tr></td></tr></table>You say, 'hail Yeolarn Bronzeleaf'<br><br>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf says 'Hail, Angelsyn ! <br>We of Tunare are charged with protecting the Great Mother from the forces of Innoruuk.  Even now, the evil minions of this foul deity are despoiling our great forest.  Will you help us [protect the Mother]? <br><br>You say, 'I will protect the Mother'<br><br>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf says 'Just outside the gates of Felwithe, the forces of Innoruuk gather in the guise of decaying skeletons.  Bring me four sets of bone chips as proof of your vigilance.  I assure you, your faith shall not go unrewarded. <br><br>Give him the bone chips<br><br>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf says 'Praise Tunare! I knew you would be victorious.  I reward you with this spell, and pray that it will help you in your fight against the unholy forces of Innoruk. When you are ready you will make a fine [Initiate of Tunare].<br><br>Your faction standing with ClericsofTunare, KingTearisthex and Anti-Mage got better.<br><br>You say, 'What Initiate of Tunare?'<br><br>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf says 'The Teir'Dal behind the undead plague in our forest have discovered a means of creating a terrible undead called a Ghast.  These Ghasts have been sighted in the Lesser Faydark and must be destroyed. Bring me four of the vile creatures hearts.<br><br>Give him four Ghast hearts! <br><br>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf says 'I requested four Ghast hearts! <br><br>Yeolarn Bronzeleaf says 'Praise Tunare!! You have done well young Initiate. Here the symbol of your station within our faith. Return to me when you are ready to [slay the necromancer] that has been creating the undead.<br> <br>Your faction standing with ClericsofTunare, KingTearisthex and Anti-Mage got better.<br>You gain party experience!!<br><br>After this, you can then do the disciple quest.</td></tr>
	 <tr><td id=rt valign=top>Reward(s):</td></tr>
	 <tr><td valign=top><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=5654">Initiate Symbol of Tunare</a></li></td></tr>
	 <tr><td colspan=2 align=center>Last modified on Thu Apr 12 16:50:05 2001</td></tr>
